&lt;h2 id="超链接">超链接&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>语法：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-csharp" data-lang="csharp">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="na">[超链接名]&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">超链接地址&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;超链接title&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">title可加可不加&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>示例：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-csharp" data-lang="csharp">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="na">[bing]&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">https&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1">//bing.com)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="na">[百度]&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">https&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1">//baidu.com)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>&lt;/tr>&lt;/table>
&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>&lt;p>效果如下：&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a class="link" href="https://bing.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>bing&lt;/a>&lt;br>
&lt;a class="link" href="https://baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>百度&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="列表">列表&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="无序列表">无序列表&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>语法：&lt;br>
无序列表用 - + * 任何一种都可以&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
&lt;table class="lntable">&lt;tr>&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code>&lt;span class="lnt">1
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">2
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">3
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">4
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="lnt">5
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/td>
&lt;td class="lntd">
&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">- 列表内容
